metadata.title: House of Fingers
metadata.name: House of Fingers
metadata.description: House of Fingers is the first claimable NFT available to holders of FuckCashGrabs. FuckCashGrabs is Josh Hart’s performative statement against celeb cash grabs in the NFT space, in partnership with Tally Labs. Originally free-to-mint, FCG adds value to holders through claimables, member-only experiences, partnerships, and more. House of Fingers was created in partnership with House of Kibaa, one of the most talented NFT studios in the space. Here’s to giving a ring to everyone with a finger and finding our inner champion.
